      <title>受美国库存增加和美联储关注影响，油价连续三天上涨后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡美国原油库存意外增加和美国货币政策前景（预计美国货币政策将在较长时间内收紧），油价在连续三天上涨后小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 23:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
